a Chosen Observable Stored in the
Data Variable</title>
      </caption>
      <graphic xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="ci0c01375_0007" id="GRAPHIC-d7e450-autogenerated" position="float"/>
    </fig>
    <fig id="sch2" position="float">
      <label>Scheme 2</label>
      <caption>
